title: Hour 2 - Tom Brady Struggles, Lakers in Trouble
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Tom Brady Struggles, Lakers in Trouble
description:
Dan Patrick examines how Tom Brady felt he struggled in all areas of the game during Thursday night's loss to the Ravens. ESPN's Laura Rutlegde joins to talk growing NFL interest in London and pitfalls for Russell Wilson and the Broncos. Sports Illustrated's Chris Mannix joins to talk Lakers troubles and more from the first week of NBA action!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
